          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Pour another one out for lightweight, gas-powered British sports cars. Lotus did what it had been talking about since it came under Chinese membership: ditching internal combustion completely. That meant releasing the Final Editions of the Elise, Exige, and Evora back in February.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
